data.description: Move in ready! This home sits on an oversized lot with a garage as well as a carport. The front deck is huge and covered so enjoy it YEAR AROUND! The bedrooms are very large and the lay out is ideal for entertaining or enjoying with your family. This home comes with a ton of positives aside from being located on a corner lot with some cool views, there is a lot of cabinetry, built ins, lots of windows, two separate living rooms,separate laundry room, a ramp onto the deck so no need to worry about stairs and much much more. Schedule a showing today!
